Feature: Gross Pay
Employee's Gross Pay is the sum of all pay for the period

Scenario Outline:
  Given an employee named <name>
  And an hourly rate of <rate> dollars
  When he works <hours> hours
  Then his gross pay should be <gross> dollars
  
  Examples:
  | name  |  rate | hours |   gross |
  | chet  | 24.00 |    40 |  960.00 |
  | ron   | 30.00 |    45 | 1350.00 |
  | sue   | 41.00 |    33 | 1353.00 |
  | grant | 27.45 | 26.75 | 734.29  |


